s%20civil%20fraud%20trial%20in%20NY.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20ex-SEC%20accountant%20offered%20blunt%20testimony%20on%20Trump's%20net-worth%20statements.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20noted%20%26quot%3Bquestionable%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0%26quot%3Bglaring%26quot%3B%20issues%20with%20the%20statements%2C%20despite%20being%20Trump's%20own%20witness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20estimates%20of%20his%20net%20worth%2C%20%26quot%3Bquestionable%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binconsistencies%26quot%3B%20are%20words%20you'd%20expect%20to%20hear%20only%20from%20his%20accuser%2C%20the%20state%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20an%20expert%20accountant%20took%20the%20stand%20in%20Trump's%20defense%20for%20a%20second%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-ny-fraud-trial-opens-today-heres-why-still-matters-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20former%20president's%20Manhattan%20fraud%20trial%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20used%20these%20very%20words%20to%20describe%20the%20creative%20math%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20certainly%20a%20red%20flag%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20testified%20the%20expert%2C%20Jason%20Flemmons%2C%20referring%20to%20an%20internal%2C%20Trump%20Organization%20spreadsheet%20from%202016%20displayed%20on%20overhead%20screens%20in%20the%20lower%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20want%20to%20know%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20said%20of%20the%20spreadsheet%2C%20in%20which%20Trump%20claimed%20some%20%24200%20million%20in%20ready%20cash.%20State%20officials%20say%20those%20millions%20were%20actually%20locked%20in%20a%20partnership%20that%20Trump%20did%20not%20have%20sole%20authority%20to%20withdraw%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20red%20flag%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20in%20the%20non-jury%20trial%2C%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%2C%20cut%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20my%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20answered%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20rather%20glaring%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20not-so-ready%20cash%20was%20just%20one%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20net-worth%20red%20flags%20identified%20Wednesday%20by%20Flemmons.%20A%20former%20fraud%20enforcer%20for%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20Flemmons%20had%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-trial-experts-offer-chillaxed-theory-of-asset-valuation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestifying%20on%20Trump's%20behalf%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20he%20described%20the%20broad%20wiggle%20room%20allowed%20in%20estimating%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20has%20alleged%20that%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Trump's%20annual%20net-worth%20statements%20fraudulently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-net-worth-math-even-fuzzier-than-ny-last-alleged-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexaggerated%20his%20worth%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%243.6%20billion%20a%20year%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eallowing%20him%20to%20reap%20at%20least%20%24250%20million%20in%20otherwise%20unavailable%20profits%20and%20interest-rate%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Flemmons%20did%20more%20Wednesday%20than%20confirm%20some%20of%20the%20attorney%20general's%20worst%20fraud%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20testified%20that%20red%20flags%20pop%20up%20routinely%20in%20the%20process%20of%20drafting%20net-worth%20statements%2C%20which%20are%20used%20by%20banks%20in%20deciding%20who%20to%20lend%20to%2C%20and%20at%20what%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happens%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20it%20certainly%20happened%20a%20lot%20in%20Trump's%20net-worth%20statements%2C%20by%20Flemmons'%20own%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELed%20through%20a%20decade%20of%20statements%20and%20underlying%20internal%20Trump%20Org%20spreadsheets%20by%20defense%20lawyer%20Jesus%20Suarez%2C%20Flemmons%20described%20numerous%20%26quot%3Bdiscrepancies%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binconsistencies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20Trump%20tripling%20the%20actual%20square%20footage%20of%20his%20Manhattan%20penthouse%2C%20his%20secretly%20adding%20a%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bbrand%20premium%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20total%20worth%2C%20and%20his%20inflating%20the%20value%20of%20Trump%20Park%20Avenue%20by%20valuing%20rent-stabilized%20condo%20units%20at%20market%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Flemmons%20deflected%20blame%20for%20these%20discrepancies%20onto%20that%20old%20Trump%20stalking%20horse%3A%20the%20outside%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20accountant's%20obligation%2C%20Flemmons%20testified%20Wednesday%2C%20to%20catch%20discrepancies%2C%20and%20not%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20person%20signing%20the%20statement%20or%20attesting%20to%20its%20truth%2C%20as%20Trump%20or%20his%20sons%20have%20done%20every%20year%20for%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20you%20have%20outside%20accountants%20involved%20in%20this%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20and%20her%20team%20of%20lawyers%20would%20%E2%80%93%20and%20have%20%E2%80%93%20begged%20to%20differ.%20It's%20just%20like%20lying%20on%20your%20taxes%2C%20they%20have%20argued%20in%20court%20and%20in%20filings%3A%20You%20can't%20dodge%20legal%20responsibility%20by%20blaming%20your%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdonald-trumps-accountants-quit-while-preparing-his-and-melanias-taxes-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20longtime%20accountant%20at%20Mazars%20USA%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Donald%20Bender%2C%20has%20pointed%20his%20finger%20right%20back%20at%20Trump.%20Bender%20said%20in%20testimony%20last%