ure%20of%20these%20moving%20average%20crossover%20strategies%2C%20which%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20generate%20false%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn't%20pay%20to%20sell%20stocks%20after%20a%20bearish%20death%20cross%20or%20buy%20stocks%20after%20a%20bullish%20golden%20cross.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftechnical-death-cross-stock-market-sp500-historical-analysis-not-bad-2022-3%5C%22%3Ea%20historical%20analysis%20by%20Fundstrat%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20death%20crosses%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20it%20pays%20to%20buy%20stocks%20after%20a%20death%20cross%2C%20rather%20than%20sell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2048%20occurrences%20since%201929%2C%20the%20average%20return%20on%20a%20three-%2C%20six-%2C%20and%2012-month%20timeframe%20were%20all%20positive%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20average%20three-month%20return%20of%202.1%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Fundstrat's%20Mark%20Newton%20said%20last%20year.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20win%20rate%20for%20a%20positive%20return%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20three%2C%20six%2C%20and%2012%20months%20after%20a%20death%20cross%20were%20all%20above%2050%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20historical%20analysis%20of%20bullish%20golden%20crosses%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201896%20also%20highlights%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20false%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technical%20buy%20indicator%20can%20sometimes%20be%20a%20head-fake%20as%20it%20has%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2064%25%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechartreport.com%2Fdoes-the-golden-cross-really-matter%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWith%2520a%252060%252D64%2525%2520success%2Cfeel%2520about%2520the%2520Golden%2520Cross%253F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20compiled%20by%20The%20Chart%20Report.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Technical%20analyst%20Ian%20McMillan%20looked%20at%20a%20total%20of%2081%20golden%20crosses%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20dating%20back%20to%20its%20inception%20in%201896.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcMillan%20found%20that%20on%20average%2C%20stocks%20were%20higher%20three%20months%20after%20a%20golden%20cross%2062%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20and%20higher%20six%20months%20after%20the%20golden%20cross%2064%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20three-month%20return%20when%20stocks%20were%20higher%20after%20a%20golden%20cross%20was%207.33%25%2C%20while%20the%20average%20return%20six%20months%20after%20the%20golden%20cross%20was%2010.65%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lagging%20nature%20of%20the%20death%20cross%20and%20golden%20cross%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20why%20technical%20analyst%20Katie%20Stockton%20of%20Fairlead%20Strategies%20isn't%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20moving%20average%20crossover%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20a%20proponent%20of%20using%20moving%20average%20crossovers%20for%20market%20timing%2Fpredictive%20value.%20They%20are%20often%20untimely%2C%20and%20simply%20tell%20us%20what%20we%20already%20know%2C%20that%20momentum%20has%20shifted%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftechnical-death-cross-stock-market-sp500-historical-analysis-not-bad-2022-3%5C%22%3EStockton%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%20data-track-content%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-post-type%3D%5C%22post%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EStressing%20the%20importance%20that%20moving%20average%20crossover%20signals%20are%20not%20perfect%2C%20Ari%20Wald%2C%20head%20of%20technical%20analysis%20at%20Oppenheimer%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20told%20The%20Chart%20Report%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20big%20rallies%20start%20with%20a%20golden%20cross%2C%20but%20not%20all%20golden%20crosses%20lead%20to%20a%20big%20rally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-dow-bearish-death-cross-bullish-golden-signal-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700081174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65551fe622cf74a573980069%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-dow-bearish-death-cross-bullish-golden-signal-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAll%20big%20rallies%20start%20with%20a%20golden%20cross%2C%20but%20not%20all%20golden%20crosses%20lead%20to%20a%20big%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20technical%20analyst%20Ari%20Wald%20of%20Oppenheimer%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-dow-bearish-death-cross-bullish-golden-signal-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20seeking%20deal%20to%20free%2050%20hostages%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700081165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105243658%2Cimgsize-1390942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fqatar-seeking-deal-to-free-50-hostages-report%2Farticleshow%2F105243636.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105243636.cms%5C%2