ficit-at-record-high-of-31-46-billion-123111500958_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexports-up-6-21-in-oct-trade-deficit-at-record-high-of-31-46-billion-123111500958_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexports-up-6-21-in-oct-trade-deficit-at-record-high-of-31-46-billion-123111500958_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narayana%20Murthy%20Says%20This%20Is%20How%20Much%20India%20Should%20Spend%20To%20Train%20Teachers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESoftware%20icon%20N%20R%20Narayana%20Murthy%20on%20Wednesday%20called%20for%20spending%20USD%20one%20billion%20a%20year%20to%20train%20school%20teachers%20by%2010%2C000%20retired%20highly%20accomplished%20teachers%20from%20the%20developed%20world%20and%20from%20India%20in%20STEM%20areas%20(Science%2C%20Technology%2C%20Engineering%20and%20Mathematics).%20This%20course%20alone%20is%20not%20sufficient%2C%20Narayana%20Murthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20show%20much%20respect%20and%20pay%20better%20salaries%20to%20our%20teachers%20and%20researchers.%20We%20must%20also%20provide%20better%20facilities%20to%20our%20researchers.%20We%20must%20honour%20them.%20They%20are%20role%20models%20for%20our%20youngsters.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20instituted%20the%20Infosys%20Prize%20in%202009.%20It%20is%20our%20small%20contribution%20to%20further%20the%20cause%20of%20research%20in%20India%26quot%3B.%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20possible%20way%20of%20accelerating%20NEP's%20(National%20Education%20Policy)%20outcome%20is%20to%20invite%2010%2C000%20retired%20highly%20accomplished%20teachers%20from%20the%20developed%20world%20and%20from%20India%20in%20STEM%20areas%20to%20create%202%2C500%20%26quot%3BTrain%20the%20Teacher%26quot%3B%20colleges%20in%20the%20country's%2028%20states%20and%20eight%20union%20territories%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20training%20programme%20should%20be%20year-long%2C%20he%20said%20in%20his%20remarks%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20where%20the%20Infosys%20Science%20Foundation%20announced%20the%20Infosys%20Prize%202023%20in%20six%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExperts%20tell%20me%20that%20each%20set%20of%20four%20trainers%20can%20train%20100%20primary%20school%20teachers%20and%20100%20secondary%20school%20teachers%20a%20year.%20We%20will%20be%20able%20to%20train%20250%2C000%20primary%20school%20teachers%20and%20250%2C000%20secondary%20school%20teachers%20every%20year%20by%20this%20method%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20founder%20of%20Infosys%20said.%20These%20trained%20Indian%20teachers%20can%20themselves%20become%20trainers%20over%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20pay%20about%20USD%20100%2C000%20a%20year%20for%20each%20of%20these%20retired%20teachers.%20This%20twenty-year%20programme%20will%20cost%20us%20USD%20one%20billion%20a%20year%20and%20USD%2020%20billion%20for%20twenty%20years.%20Our%20nation%2C%20targeting%20a%20GDP%20of%20USD%20five%20trillion%20soon%2C%20will%20not%20find%20it%20a%20big%20financial%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murthy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20trustee%20of%20Infosys%20Science%20Foundation%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20this%20is%20expensive%2C%20you%20may%20recall%20the%20words%20of%20Derek%20Bok%2C%20a%20former%20President%20of%20Harvard%20University%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20education%20is%20expensive%2C%20try%20ignorance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20the%20Infosys%20Science%20Foundation%20will%20be%20making%20a%20strong%20recommendation%20on%20teachers'%20training%20and%20spending%20towards%20it%2C%20amid%20increased%20allocations%20on%20freebies%20by%20some%20governments%20and%20cut%20in%20budget%20on%20science%20and%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20Murthy%20said%2C%20he%20has%20made%20the%20suggestion%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20there%20are%20experts%20who%20will%20evaluate%20it%20and%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20environment%20like%20India's%20there%20are%20always%20suggestions%20by%20various%20people%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20we%20have%20a%20set%20of%20experts%20who%20will%20evaluate%20those%20suggestions.%20And%20if%20it%20is%20found%20to%20be%20worthwhile%2C%20they%20may%20take%20it%20forward.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20won't%2C%20that's%20natural.%20And%20therefore%2C%20I%20think%20all%20these%20suggestions%20should%20be%20welcomed%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20given%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Infosys%20co-founder%20and%20President%2C%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20of%20the%20foundation%20S%20Gopalakrishnan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20our%20GDP%20grows%2C%20we%20need%20to%20do%20something%20different%20and%20we%20can't%20continue%20the%20same%20way%20that%20we%20are%20progressing.%26quot%3B%20Pointing%20at%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%202020%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20would%20like%20to%20see%20faster%20implementation%20of%20that%20policy.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20that%20we%20make%20a%20recommendation%2C%20its%20implementation%20is%20equally%20important.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20that%20spirit%20that%20Mr.%20Murthy%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20has%20made%20this%20recommendation.%26quot%3B%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20in%20his%20remarks%20highlighted%20that%20there%20are%20four%20stages%20in%20the%20invention%20and%20innovation%20lifecycle%20of%20a%20nation%20and%20said%20countries%20progress%20from%20stage%20one%20to%20stage%20four%20using%20education%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20success%20in%20atomic%20energy%2C%20space%20exploration%2C%20vaccine%20production%20and%20distribution%2C%20green%20revolution%2C%20electric%20cars%2C%20and%20generic%20medicines%20puts%20us%20in%20stage%20two%20in%20most%20areas%20and%20in%20stage%20three%20in%20a%20few%20areas%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20in%20stage%20one%20in%20some%20important%20areas%20like%20design%20of%20livable%20cities%2C%20pollution%20management%2C%20traffic%20management%2C%20and%20providing%20clean%20and%20safe%20water.%26quot%3B%20India%20must%20aspire%20to%20move%20to%20stage%20four%20in%20every%20area%20that%20affects%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20poorest%20citizens%20in%20the%20remotest%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20research%20and%20education%20in%20our%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning%20to%20generate%20good%20ideas%20and%20focusing%20on%20quick%20and%20high-quality%20implementation%20of%20those%20ideas%20form%20the%20solution%20to%20this%20aspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcellence%20in%20speed%20in%20idea%20generation%20and%20in%20execution%20of%20those%20ideas%20comes%20from%20a%20culture%20of%20high%20aspiration%2C%20curious%20and%20inquiring%20minds%2C%20a%20desire%20to%20achieve%20the%20best%20global%20standard%20of%20work%20productivity%2C%20the%20most%20stringent%20discipline%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20the%20mindset%20of%20a%20nation%20that%20respects%20better-performing%20cultures%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20learn%20from%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitching%20for%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20primary%2C%20secondary%2C%20and%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20to%20embrace%20independent%2C%20critical%2C%20and%20analytical%20thinking%3B%20%26quot%3BSocratic%20questioning%26quot%3B%3B%20and%20focusing%20on%20relating%20theory%20to%20understand%20the%20real%20world%20around%20us%3B%20to%20solve%20the%20mysteries%20of%20nature%3B%20and%20to%20solve%20our%20real-world%20problems%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20NEP%20has%20started%20this%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700069880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-04%2Fnarayan-murthy_650x400_41491196005.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-spend-1-billion-annually-to-train-teachers-narayana-murthy-4575879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Software%20icon%20N%20R%20Narayana%20Murthy%20on%20Wednesday%20called%20for%20spending%20USD%20one%20billion%20a%20year%20to%20train%20school%20teachers%20by%2010%2C000%20retired%20highly%20accomplished%20teachers%20from%20the%20developed%20world%20and%20from%20India%20in%20STEM%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-spend-1-billion-annually-to-train-teachers-narayana-murthy-4575879%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-spend-1-billion-annually-to-train-teachers-narayana-murthy-4575879%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-spend-1-billion-annually-to-train-teachers-narayana-murthy-4575879%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Persuades%20Nine%20Rebels%20To%20Drop%20Out%20Of%20Telangana%20Race%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20Congress%20appears%20to%20have%20managed%20to%20convince%20nine%20rebels%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20electoral%20race%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20nominations.%20The%20rebels%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20nominations%20after%20failing%20to%20obtain%20tickets%20from%20the%20party%20to%20contest%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20have%20withdrawn%20in%20favour%20of%20official%20candidates.%20Adilabad%20is%20the%20only%20exception%20where%20rebel%20Congress%20candidate%20Sanjeev%20Reddy%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20electoral%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20say%20with%20the%20experience%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20party%20put%20in%20place%20specific%20teams%20to%20talk%20to%20rebel%20candidates%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20withdraw.%20They%20were%20offered%20other%20posts%20or%20an%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20high%20drama%20at%20the%20home%20of%20Patel%20Ramesh%20Reddy%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20nomination%20from%20Suryapet%2C%20when%20AICC%20national%20secretary%20Rohit%20Chaudhary%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Mallu%20Ravi%20went%20to%20visit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20meant%20to%20request%20him%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20race%20and%20support%20the%20party's%20official%20candidate%20Ramreddy%20Damodar%20Reddy.%20But%20supporters%20of%20Patel%20Ramesh%20Reddy%20grew%20violent%20and%20attacked%2073-year-old%20Mallu%20Ravi%20after%20his%20request%20for%20a%20tete-e-tete.%20Inside%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20others%20were%20seen%20crying%20and%20pleading%20with%20the%20leaders%20to%20support%20his%20candidature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20finally%20withdrew%20from%20the%20race%20after%20he%20was%20told%20he%20would%20be%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20parliament%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20Ramesh%20Reddy%20was%20denied%20ticket%20in%202018%20as%20well.%20When%20the%20list%20was%20announced%20this%20time%2C%20a%20video%20had%20gone%20viral%20where%20he%20and%20his%20family%20were%20seen%20breaking%20down%2C%20wailing%20that%20this%20was%20happening%20to%20them%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20too%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20told%20that%20he%20would%20be%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20parliamentary%20elections%20from%20Nalgonda.%20But%20instead%2C%20Huzurnagar%20MLA%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20contested%20and%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamreddy%20Damodar%20Reddy%20had%20been%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20YSR%20cabinet%20and%20lost%20the%20election%20to%20Jagadish%20Reddy%20of%20the%20BRS%20in%202018%20and%20in%202014.%20He%20had%20moved%20from%20Thungathurthi%20where%20he%20was%20MLA%20multiple%20times%20and%20was%20seen%20to%20have%20been%20backed%20by%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20and%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%20--%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20got%20elected%20as%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20Ramesh%20Reddy%20crossed%20over%20to%20Congress%20from%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20along%20with%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20before%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20move%20to%20deny%20him%20a%20ticket%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20fight%20for%20dominance%20between%20the%20Revanth%20Reddy%20camp%20and%20the%20Reddy%20leaders%20in%20the%20Congress%20from%20before%20his%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20deadline%20to%20withdraw%20nominations%20ending%20today%2C%20the%20battlelines%20are%20now%20drawn%20for%20the%20day%20of%20voting%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20figures%20shared%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20Telangana%20has%20over%203.26%20crore%20eligible%20voters%20with%20almost%20equal%20number%20of%20men%20and%20women.%20Serilingampally%20segment%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20voters%20with%20over%207.32%20lakh%20while%20Bhadrachalam%20registered%20the%20lowest%20with%201.49%20lakh%20electors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20officials%20have%20found%202%2C898%20nominations%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20November%2030%20assembly%20elections%20to%20be%20valid%20before%20withdrawal%20and%20rejected%20nominations%20of%20606%20candidates%20during%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700069700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2F4nod8ekk_telangana-congress-leaders-650_625x300_13_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-assembly-election-2023-nine-congress-rebels-drop-out-of-telangana-race-4577632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Te