after%20several%20reports%20suggested%20that%20the%20hosts%20have%20changed%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20order%20to%20assist%20their%20spinners.%20The%20reports%20said%20that%20although%20a%20new%20deck%20was%20prepared%20for%20the%20match%2C%20the%20match%20was%20ultimately%20played%20on%20a%20'used%20surface'.%20After%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E%20guided%20India%20to%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20with%20a%20win%20over%20New%20Zealand%2C%20legendary%20India%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20fumed%20over%20the%20rumours%20and%20rubbished%20any%20such%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20morons%20who%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20pitch%20change.%20Just%20stop.%20Stop%20taking%20potshots%20at%20Indian%20cricket.%20People%20have%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20to%20attract%20eyeballs%20or%20whatever.%20It%20is%20all%20nonsense.%20The%20pitch%20was%20there%20and%20even%20if%20it%20was%20changed%2C%20it%20was%20there%20before%20the%20toss%20for%20both%20the%20teams.%20It%20was%20not%20changed%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20innings.%20It%20was%20not%20changed%20after%20the%20toss%20was%20done.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20good%20enough%20team%2C%20you%20play%20on%20that%20pitch%20and%20you%20win.%20India%20has%20done%20that.%20So%20stop%20talking%20about%20pitches.%20Already%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20second%20semifinal%20hasn't%20even%20taken%20place.%20They%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20pitch%20being%20changed%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Nonsense%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20issued%20a%20statement%20regarding%20the%20entire%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChanges%20to%20planned%20pitch%20rotations%20are%20common%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20an%20event%20of%20this%20length%2C%20and%20have%20already%20happened%20a%20couple%20of%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20change%20was%20made%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20venue%20curator%20in%20conjunction%20with%20our%20host%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20also%20said%20Atkinson%2C%20its%20independent%20pitch%20consultant%2C%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20independent%20pitch%20consultant%20was%20apprised%20of%20the%20change%20and%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20the%20pitch%20won't%20play%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20ICC's%20Playing%20Conditions%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20host%20association%20is%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20for%20the%20selection%20and%20preparation%20of%20the%20pitch%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20no%20requirement%20that%20a%20knockout%20match%20must%20be%20played%20on%20fresh%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700069340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fofakngdg_virat-kohli_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fall-the-morons-sunil-gavaskars-explosive-take-on-pitch-change-nonsense-in-cricket-world-cup-2023-4577618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20fume