0unexplained%20payments%20made%20to%20allegedly%20fake%20human%20resource%20consultancies%20by%20co-founder%20Ashneer%20Grover%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20the%20company's%20former%20head%20of%20controls%20Madhuri%20Jain%20Grover%20as%20well%20as%20Madhuri%20Jain's%20family%20members%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20allegedly%20used%20backdated%20invoices%20to%20move%20funds%20from%20BharatPe's%20accounts%20for%20payment%20of%20commissions%20for%20recruitment%20work%2C%20a%20status%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20EOW%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20Rs%207.6%20crore%20was%20paid%20to%20allegedly%20fake%20HR%20consultancies%2C%20while%20Rs%201.66%20crore%20was%20paid%20as%20penalty%20to%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20authorities.%20Another%20Rs%2071.76%20crore%20was%20allegedly%20siphoned%20off%20via%20fictitious%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20amount%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20these%20transactions%20could%20be%20well%20over%20Rs%2081%20crore%2C%20as%20the%20EOW%20investigation%20is%20still%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%20status%20report%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%2C%20scrutiny%20of%20A%2Fc%20No.%20%5Bredacted%5D%20(belonging%20to%20alleged%20Madhuri%20Jain%2FGrover)%20revealed%20that%20she%20got%20huge%20amount%20of%20approx.%20Rs%205%20crore%2C%20Rs%203%20crore%20and%20Rs%202%20crore%20from%20her%20father%20Suresh%20Jain%2C%20mother%20Santosh%20Jain%20and%20brother%20Shwetank%20Jain%2C%20respectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20Jain%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20controls%20at%20BharatPe%2C%20was%20fired%20in%202022%20after%20a%20forensic%20audit%20revealed%20several%20irregularities.%20Subsequently%2C%20Ashneer%20Grover%20resigned%20as%20CEO%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20scrutiny%20of%20account%20no.%20%5Bredacted%5D%20(belonging%20to%20alleged%20Ashneer%20Grover)%20revealed%20that%20the%20petitioner%20Ashneer%20Grover%20transferred%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2046%20crore%20(approx.)%20in%20the%20account%20of%20his%20father%20Ashok%20Grover%20from%202019%20to%202022.%20These%20huge%20transactions%20are%20to%20be%20verified%20and%20their%20purpose%2Fend%20user%20to%20be%20ascertained%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EOW%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%20had%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20earlier%20this%20year%20under%20eight%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20criminal%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20cheating%20and%20dishonesty%2C%20and%20forgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharatPe%2C%20in%20its%20complaint%2C%20alleged%20that%20Ashneer%20Grover%20and%20his%20family%20caused%20damages%20of%20about%20Rs%2081.3%20crore%20through%20illegitimate%20payments%20to%20allegedly%20fake%20human%20resource%20consultants%2C%20among%20other%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700068080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F8n3h9tt_ashneer-grover_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharatpe-ex-ceo-ashneer-grover-family-made-fake-multi-crore-invoices-sources-4577524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing's%20(EOW)%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20fraud%20at%20payments%20firm%20BharatPe%20has%20found%20a%20host%20of%20unexplained%20payments%20made%20to%20allegedly%20fake%20human%20resource%20consultancies%20by%20co-founder%20Ashneer%20Grover%20and%20his%20wife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharatpe-ex-ceo-ashneer-grover-family-made-fake-multi-crore-invoices-sources-4577524%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharatpe-ex-ceo-ashneer-grover-family-made-fake-multi-crore-invoices-sources-4577524%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A