0deep...%20Having%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20our%20Matty%20has%20been%20an%20insane%20wave%20of%20emotions%20that%20I've%20never%20experienced%20before.%20We%20all%20experience%20loss%20at%20some%20point%20in%20our%20lives.%20Loss%20of%20life%20or%20loss%20of%20love.%20Being%20able%20to%20really%20SIT%20in%20this%20grief%20allows%20you%20to%20feel%20the%20moments%20of%20joy%20and%20gratitude%20for%20having%20loved%20someone%20that%20deep.%20And%20we%20loved%20him%20deeply.%20He%20was%20such%20a%20part%20of%20our%20DNA.%20We%20were%20always%20the%206%20of%20us.%20This%20was%20a%20chosen%20family%20that%20forever%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20who%20we%20were%20and%20what%20our%20path%20was%20going%20to%20be.%20For%20Matty%2C%20he%20KNEW%20he%20loved%20to%20make%20people%20laugh.%20As%20he%20said%20himself%2C%20if%20he%20didn't%20hear%20the%20%E2%80%98laugh'%20he%20thought%20he%20was%20going%20to%20die.%20His%20life%20literally%20depended%20on%20it.%20And%20boy%20did%20he%20succeed%20in%20doing%20just%20that.%20He%20made%20all%20of%20us%20laugh.%20And%20laugh%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20contInued%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20couple%20weeks%2C%20I've%20been%20pouring%20over%20our%20texts%20to%20one%20another.%20Laughing%20and%20crying%20then%20laughing%20again.%20I'll%20keep%20them%20forever%20and%20ever.%20I%20found%20one%20text%20that%20he%20sent%20me%20out%20of%20nowhere%20one%20day.%20It%20says%20it%20all.%20(See%20the%20second%20slide%E2%80%A6).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJennifer%20signed%20off%20the%20post%20with%20a%20famous%20phrase%20by%20Mathew%20Perry.%20It%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BMatty%2C%20I%20love%20you%20so%20much%20and%20I%20know%20you%20are%20now%20completely%20at%20peace%20and%20out%20of%20any%20pain.%20I%20talk%20to%20you%20every%20day%E2%80%A6%20sometimes%20I%20can%20almost%20hear%20you%20saying%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20you%20BE%20any%20crazier%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rest%20little%20brother.%20You%20always%20made%20my%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2F