gested%20by%20the%20police%2C%20the%20report%20stated%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20stoked%20anger%20among%20the%20affected%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalsa%20Vox%20quoted%20an%20observer%20as%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20attack%20on%20Diwali%20celebrations%20in%20Brampton%2C%20Canada.%20It%20is%20also%20concerning%20that%20the%20Canadian%20media%20is%20downplaying%20the%20incident%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20'fight%20between%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus.'%20This%20attack%20was%20motivated%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists%20to%20incite%20religious%20hatred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Khalsa%20Vox%2C%20the%20alleged%20display%20of%20Khalistani%20flags%20during%20the%20attack%20adds%20to%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20Canada%20is%20unintentionally%20or%20knowingly%20providing%20a%20platform%20for%20extremist%20elements%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20Khalistan%20cause%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Canadian%20natives%20are%20rising%20with%20frustration%20as%20they%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20presence%20of%20Khalistani%20elements%20in%20their%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20renowned%20for%20its%20commitment%20to%20inclusivity%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20and%20peace%2C%20however%2C%20is%20currently%20facing%20a%20challenge%20as%20some%20individuals%20associated%20with%20the%20Khalistani%20movement%20are%20accused%20of%20inciting%20violence%2C%20spreading%20hatred%2C%20and%20contributing%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20crimes%2C%20Khalsa%20Vox%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20incident%20has%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20Ottawa%20to%20critically%20assess%20its%20stance%20on%20Khalistan%20and%20the%20potential%20impact%20it%20may%20have%20on%20social%20harmony%20within%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20during%20the%20Diwali%20celebration%20in%20Canada%20brings%20attention%20to%20the%20delicate%20balance%20Canada%20must%20navigate%20between%20supporting%20the%20rights%20of%20its%20citizens%20to%20express%20their%20views%20and%20ensuring%20that%20such%20expressions%20do%20not%20morph%20into%20violent%20acts%20against%20other%20communities%2C%20Khalsa%20Vox%20noted%20further%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20maintaining%20the%20right%20to%20free%20expression%2C%20it%20is%20equally%20important%20for%20Canada%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20activities%20of%20groups%20that%20may%20exploit%20these%20freedoms%20to%20spread%20hatred%20and%20engage%20in%20violent%20actions%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20serves%20as%20a%20timely%20reminder%20to%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20to%20reevaluate%20their%20policies%20and%20take%20decisive%20action%20to%20prevent%20the%20escalation%20of%20religiously%20motivated%20violence%20within%20their%20borders%2C%20the%20report%20stated%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700064240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ftused1s8_khalistani-flag-generic_120x90_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgroups-carrying-khalistani-flags-disrupt-canada-diwali-festivities-throw-stones-report-4577250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Groups%20allegedly%20carrying%20Khalistani%20flags%20gate-crashed%20the%20Diwali%20festivities%20in%20Canada's%20Brampton%20and%20started%20hurling%20stones%20at%20the%20people%20celebrating%20the%20festival%2C%20Khalsa%20Vox%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgroups-carrying-khalistani-flags-disru