20report%20of%20the%20last%20public%20All%20India%20Caste%20Census%20conducted%20in%201931%20which%20no%20longer%20exist.%20At%20least%20they%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20Bihar%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20of%202022%20released%20by%20Bihar%20government.%20One%20of%20these%20castes%20groups%20is%20the%20Gorkan%20which%20is%20missing%20in%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20caste%20which%20has%20exactly%20the%20same%20status%20in%20Islam%20as%20the%20Dom%20caste%20group%20does%20in%20Hinduism.%20The%20way%20the%20deceased%20in%20Hindu%20religion%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98liberated%E2%80%99%20only%20through%20the%20fire%20ignited%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20someone%20belonging%20to%20the%20Dom%20caste%2C%20the%20dead%20in%20Islam%20are%20laid%20to%20rest%20owing%20to%20the%20labour%20of%20a%20Gorkan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEtymologically%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egorkan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20Persian%20word%20where%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20grave%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20suffix%20for%20digger.%20Gorkan%20are%20gravediggers.%20The%20moment%20someone%20dies%2C%20a%20Gorkan%20is%20the%20first%20to%20be%20informed.%20He%20digs%20the%20grave%20at%20the%20place%20specified%20by%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased.%20But%20their%20work%20is%20not%20over%20with%20just%20digging%20graves.%20They%20are%20the%20last%20to%20leave%20after%20a%20deceased%20person%20has%20been%20buried%20as%20they%20have%20to%20fill%20the%20grave%20and%20level%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20discrimination%20in%20Islam%20in%20terms%20of%20religion%20but%20there%20is%20segregation%20based%20on%20social%20status.%20For%20example%2C%20Ashraf%20are%20those%20who%20have%20land%2C%20property%20and%20prestige.%20They%20include%20Sheikh%2C%20Syed%2C%20Mughal%20and%20Pathan.%20The%20second%20are%20Azlaf%20which%20are%20communities%20offering%20various%20services%20such%20as%20carpenters%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebarhai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20barbers%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enaayi)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20tailors%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eidrisi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20dyers%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erangrez%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20etc.%20One%20might%20equate%20them%20with%20the%20backward%20classes%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitutional%20system.%20There%20is%20no%20stigma%20of%20untouchability%20associated%20with%20these%20communities%20but%20the%20third%20category%20of%20Arzal%20communities%20is%20treated%20disparagingly%20even%20today.%20They%20include%20Lalbeggi%2C%20Halalkhor%20and%20Gorkan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Gorkan%20community%20are%20no%20longer%20there%20in%20Bihar%2C%20at%20least%20not%20according%20to%20the%20statistics%20in%20the%20survey.%20Does%20it%20mean%20the%20caste%20has%20become%20extinct%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20then%20who%20digs%20graves%20now%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20is%20that%20Gorkans%20are%20still%20there%20but%20the%20changing%20economy%20has%20forced%20them%20to%20switch%20professions.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Gorkan%20community%20used%20to%20get%20religious%20protection%20and%20thrived%20on%20charity.%20As%20long%20as%20this%20system%20was%20in%20place%2C%20they%20stuck%20with%20their%20identity.%20But%20with%20time%2C%20this%20protection%20ended%20and%20other%20castes%20took%20over%20the%20task%20of%20digging%20graves%2C%20primarily%20the%20Nutt%20community.%20This%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20interesting%20castes%20of%20Bihar.%20They%20are%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20present%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Hindu%20Nutts%20is%201%2C05%2C368%20and%20that%20of%20Muslim%20Nutts%20is%2061%2C629.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20people%20of%20Gorkan%20community%20have%20changed%20their%20caste%20after%20changing%20their%20profession%20like%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Nutt%20caste.%20But%20this%20possibility%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260825%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-gorkans%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%5C%22%3ERangrez%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href