dio-Pulmonary%20Resuscitation)%20by%20his%20son%20at%20Taj%20Mahal%20is%20being%20widely%20circulated%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20who%20came%20with%20his%20family%20to%20see%20Taj%2C%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20while%20inside%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20son%20immediately%20gave%20him%20CPR%2C%20which%20many%20recorded%20on%20their%20cellphones.%20The%20live%20video%20has%20now%20gone%20viral%2C%20underscoring%20the%20importance%20of%20learning%20such%20basic%20first%20aid%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20recovered%20after%20a%20while%20and%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20details%20are%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPR%20keeps%20a%20person's%20blood%20flowing%20until%20healthcare%20professionals%20arrive%20to%20help.%20Even%20people%20without%20formal%20first%20aid%20training%20can%20save%20a%20life%20by%20using%20CPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20give%20CPR%2C%20place%20the%20person%20on%20his%20back%20in%20a%20safe%20area%20and%20tilt%20his%20head%20back%20slightly%20by%20lifting%20the%20chin.%20Open%20his%20mouth%20and%20check%20for%20obstruction%2C%20such%20as%20food%20or%20vomit.%20Carefully%20remove%20obstruction%20if%20there%20is%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlace%20your%20ear%20next%20to%20the%20person's%20mouth%20and%20listen%20for%2010%20seconds.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20hear%20breathing%2C%20or%20hear%20occasional%20gasps%2C%20begin%20CPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlace%20one%20of%20your%20hands%20on%20top%20of%20the%20other%20and%20clasp%20them%20together.%20With%20the%20heel%20of%20the%20hands%20and%20straight%20elbows%2C%20push%20hard%20and%20fast%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20chest%2C%20slightly%20below%20the%20nipples.%20Push%20at%20least%202%20inches%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20sure%20his%20mouth%20is%20clear%2C%20tilt%20their%20head%20back%20slightly%20and%20lift%20his%20chin.%20Pinch%20his%20nose%20shut%2C%20seal%20your%20mouth%20over%20his%2C%20and%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20his%20chest%20does%20not%20rise%20with%20the%20first%20breath%2C%20tilt%20his%20head%20again%20properly.%20If%20their%20chest%20still%20does%20not%20rise%20with%20a%20second%20breath%2C%20the%20person%20might%20be%20choking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20breath%20should%20last%20about%201%20second%20and%20makes%20the%20chest%20rise%2C%20allow%20air%20to%20exit%20before%20giving%20the%20next%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompress%20chest%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20least%20100%20or%20120%20times%20a%20minute.%20Let%20the%20chest%20get%20back%20to%20normal%20position%20between%20compressions.%20Repeat%20the%20cycle%20of%2030%20chest%20compressions%20and%20two%20rescue%20breaths%20until%20the%20person%20starts%20breathing%20or%20help%20arrives%20and%20takes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20CPR%20is%20done%20immediately%20after%20someone's%20heart%20stops%20beating%2C%20it%20can%20double%20or%20even%20triple%20the%20chances%20of%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700058960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fd5lq43j8_taj-mahal-cpr-by-man_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-man-gives-cpr-to-father-at-taj-mahal-saves-his-life-4576998%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20of%20a%20tourist%20being%20given%20CPR%20(Cardio-Pulmonary%20Resuscitation)%20by%20his%20son%20at%20Taj%20Mahal%20is%20being%20widely%20circulated%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-man-gives-cpr-to-father-at-taj-mahal-saves-his-life-4576998%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-man-gives-cpr-to-father-at-taj-mahal-saves-his-life-4576998%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-man-gives-cpr-to-father-at-taj-mahal-saves-his-life-4576998%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20As%20Xi-Biden%20Meet%20After%20a%20Year%2C%20Both%20Sides%20Play%20Nice%2C%20but%20Expectations%20Are%20Low%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15194439%2Fimage-1506.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20they%20meet%20today%20in%20California%2C%20each%20and%20every%20second%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20would%20have%20been%20mapped%20out.%20The%20intricate%20choreography%20highlights%20the%20delicate%20nature%20of%20their%20relations%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20cautious%20in%20not%20raising%20any%20hopes%20of%20any%20substantive%20takeaway%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20there%20is%20buzz%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20reopening%20military%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20meeting%20significant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20China%20are%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20two%20largest%20economies%2C%20but%20the%20APEC%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20their%20leaders%20would%20be%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20in%20over%20a%20year.%20Last%20time%2C%20Xi%20and%20Biden%20had%20met%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%20Bali%20in%20November%202022%20for%20about%20three%20hours.%20The%20US%20leader%20had%20hoped%20to%20talk%20with%20Xi%20during%20the%202023%20G-20%20summit%20in%20India%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese%20President%20was%20a%20no-show%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20has%20China%20been%20signalling%20its%20intent%20before%20the%20meeting%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20former%20Obama%20administration%20official%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chinese%20state%20commentaries%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20visit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fw