ers%20who%20feed%20us.%20How%20can%20we%20allow%20the%20destruction%20of%20our%20mother%20by%20mining%3F%20It%20will%20pollute%20the%20environment%20and%20displace%20us%20from%20our%20lands%20and%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20also%20questioned%20the%20Odisha%20police%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20whose%20protection%20are%20you%20there%3F%20Us%2C%20the%20people%2C%20or%20a%20private%20company%20like%20Vedanta%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20distressed%20and%20agonized%20Laxmi%20Nayak(45)%20from%20Banteji%20also%20wanted%20to%20question%20the%20police%20at%20the%20public%20hearing.%20Laxmi%20wanted%20to%20share%20her%20grief%20and%20concerns%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20speak.%20Her%20partner%2C%20Tankadhar%20Nayak%2C%20an%20elder%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijimali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20is%20being%20hounded%20by%20the%20police%20for%20opposing%20the%20mines.%20Tankadhar%20had%20to%20flee%20to%20the%20forests%20with%20fellow%20villagers%20to%20avoid%20police%20repression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164147%2Funnamed-11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164147%2Funnamed-11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164147%2Funnamed-11-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164147%2Funnamed-11-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684907%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%207%2C%20around%20