me%20thinking%20about%20my%20own%20upbringing%20and%20the%20caste-class%20system%20surrounding%20us.%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%20and%20change%20the%20way%20we%20look%20at%20dignity%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20returning%20to%20his%20homeland%2C%20Vishal%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20his%20weekends%20to%20meaningful%20volunteer%20work.%20He%20focused%20on%20assisting%20youth%20from%20underprivileged%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F239494%2Fonline-education-classes-how-to-volunteer-covid19-distance-teaching-ngos-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evulnerable%20backgrounds%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20they%20were%20exposed%20to%20issues%20such%20as%20malnutrition%2C%20abuse%2C%20and%20exposure%20to%20crime%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20Education%20and%20life%20skills%20were%20not%20prioritised%20for%20this%20group%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20offer%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20various%20connections%2C%20he%20met%20a%20group%20of%20passionate%20people%2C%20all%20in%20their%20early%2020s%20working%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20Although%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20specifically%20know%20each%20other%2C%20they%20shared%20a%20common%20goal%20to%20build%20a%20roadmap%20that%20would%20give%20them%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20Vishal%20and%20a%20team%20of%2010%20others%20established%20%E2%80%98Dream%20a%20Dream%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20transforming%20the%20life%20experience%20of%20vulnerable%20children%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdream-a-dream-5-1700039356.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20us