0spot%20where%20the%20labourers%20are%20trapped%20in%2010-12%20hours.%20The%20pipe%20has%20a%20diameter%20of%20900%20mm%2C%20which%20will%20be%20enough%20for%20the%20men%20to%20squeeze%20through%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20machine%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%20late%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20it%20could%20be%20installed%20and%20work%20could%20begin%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20it%20arrives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECave%20Expertise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20have%20contacted%20a%20company%20from%20Thailand%20which%20had%20helped%20save%20a%20junior%20association%20football%20team%20that%20was%20trapped%20in%20Tham%20Luang%20Nang%20Non%2C%20a%20cave%20system%20in%20Chiang%20Rai%20province%2C%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20in%202018.%20That%20rescue%20effort%20took%20over%20a%20week%20and%20involved%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people%20and%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20the%20company's%20expertise%20will%20be%20invaluable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelp%20is%20also%20being%20taken%20from%20the%20Norwegian%20Geotechnical%20Institute%20for%20suggestions%20on%20how%20to%20carry%20out%20operations%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20Such%20suggestions%20are%20also%20being%20taken%20from%20experts%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20and%20bodies%20affiliated%20to%20it%20such%20as%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited%2C%20Rail%20India%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Service%20(RITES)%20and%20Indian%20Railway%20Construction%20International%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshu%20Manish%20Khalkho%2C%20Director%2C%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20machine%20is%20on%20the%20way%20and%20should%20arrive%20soon.%20In%20three-four%20hours%2C%20we%20can%20begin%20work%20with%20it.%20Debris%20is%20being%20removed%20but%20some%20of%20it%20is%20being%20replaced%20by%20more%20falling%20debris.%20So%2C%20that%20is%20not%20our%20focus.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20push%20the%20pipe%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Labourers%20Okay'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20machine%20can%20push%20the%20pipe%20about%203-4%20metres%20in%20an%20hour%20and%20we%20can%20finish%20the%20work%20in%2010-12%20hours%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20what%20machines%20are%20stuck%20inside.%20The%20labourers%20are%20fine%2C%20they%20are%20getting%20food%20and%20their%20families%20and%20officials%20are%20speaking%20to%20them%20to%20keep%20their%20morale%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khalkho%20said%20they%20have%20a%20backup%20plan%20in%20place%20even%20if%20this%20machine%20does%20not%20work%20and%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20put%20a%20timeframe%20on%20the%20rescue%20plan.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20us%20are%20as%20worried%20as%20the%20families%20of%20the%20labourers%20and%20no%20one%20is%20resting%20until%20we%20rescue%20our%20brothers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20family%20members%20and%20other%20labourers%20also%20held%20a%20protest%20near%20the%20site%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20rescuing%20the%20trapped%20men.%20Mr%20Khalkho%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20protesters%20and%20claimed%20they%20have%20understood%20the%20situation%20and%20agreed%20to%20help%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20the%204.5-km%20tunnel%20on%20the%20Brahmakhal-Yamunotri%20National%20Highway%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20join%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%20collapsed%20early%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%20The%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700054520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjoqmr1a8_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-call-made-to-firm-that-saved-thai-children-from-cave-4576789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20la