y%20concerned%20citizens%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDate%3A%2015.11.2023%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20concerned%20citizens%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20express%20our%20anguish%20and%20distress%20at%20the%20way%20Ms%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20a%20distinguished%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20has%20been%20treated%20for%20raising%20genuine%20concerns%20about%20a%20corporate%20group%E2%80%99s%20activities%20that%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20public%20interest%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20news%20reports%20(https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Flok-sabha-ethics-panel-suggests-disqualification-for-tmc-mp-mahua-moitra%2Farticle67516744.ece)%2C%20we%20understand%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20may%20face%20expulsion%20from%20the%20Parliament%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20certain%20allegations%20which%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20subjected%20to%20strict%20Parliamentary%20and%20judicial%20scrutiny%20in%20compliance%20with%20established%20norms%20of%20natural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20larger%20issues%20that%20arise%20from%20this%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20necessity%20of%20the%20political%20executive%20remaining%20accountable%20to%20the%20Parliament%20and%20the%20public%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20feel%20that%20the%20issues%20arising%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%20cannot%20be%20viewed%20narrowly%20as%20being%20an%20inter-corporate%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20They%20are%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20issues%20arising%20in%20the%20case%20of%20one%20corporate%20entity%20and%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20Unless%20those%20issues%20are%20examined%20as%20outlined%20below%20in%20their%20entirety%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20Parliament%20will%20be%20doing%20a%20grave%20injustice%20to%20itself%20and%20also%20to%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20there%20are%20reports%20of%20a%20corporate%20entity%20failing%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20established%20norms%20of%20corporate%20governance%2C%20should%20the%20executive%20and%2For%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20as%20demanded%20by%20several%20political%20parties%2C%20instead%20of%20enquiring%20into%20the%20veracity%20of%20those%20reports%20and%20placing%20the%20facts%20before%20the%20Parliament%20and%20the%20public%2C%20use%20its%20power%20of%20privilege%20with%20is%20meant%20for%20public%20good%20to%20question%20those%20who%20raise%20those%20concerns%2C%20intimidate%20them%20and%20gag%20dissent%3F%20Does%20not%20such%20conduct%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20executive%20hurt%20the%20public%20interest%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20time%2C%20the%20Companies%20Act%20prohibited%20corporate%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20As%20electoral%20corruption%20and%20profligacy%20in%20election%20expenditure%20started%20increasing%2C%20successive%20governments%20chose%20to%20dilute%20that%20Act%20to%20permit%20private%20companies%20to%20fund%20elections.%20During%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20present%20government%20went%20far%20beyond%20that%20and%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20to%20corporate%20donations%2C%20including%20donations%20from%20foreign%20sources.%20As%20if%20that%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20it%20introduced%20a%20highly%20regressive%20system%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20that%20have%20permitted%20political%20parties%20to%20receive%20donations%20from%20anonymous%20individuals%20and%20corporate%20bodies%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20deprived%20the%20citizens%20of%20their%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20know%E2%80%9D%20under%20Article%2019%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20has%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20private%20companies%20to%20fund%20the%20political%20parties%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20influence%20them%20to%20grant%20them%20quid%20pro%20quos%20in%20terms%20of%20dilution%20of%20environmental%20and%20other%20laws%20and%20compromising%20institutions%20to%20suit%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20responded%20to%20questions%20on%20instances%20of%20irregularities%20in%20corporate%20governance%20highlights%20the%20strong%20nexus%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20big%20businesses%20and%20its%20deleterious%20implications%20for%20the%20public%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20the%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%20brought%20to%20light%20many%20issues%20of%20importance%20that%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20would%20never%20have%20been%20privy%20to.%20Her%20THREATENED%20exit%20from%20the%20Parliament%20will%20certainly%20create%20a%20void%20in%20the%20continuing%20discourse%20on%20such%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20specific%20reference%20to%20the%20matter%20concerning%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20place%20on%20record%20the%20following%20concerns%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Natural%20justice%20requires%20that%20a%20person%20facing%20an%20accusation%20be%20given%20adequate%20opportunity%20to%20have%20access%20to%20all%20evidence%20put%20forward%20in%20support%20of%20such%20an%20accusation%2C%20cross-examine%20witnesses%2C%20if%20any%2C%20who%20have%20made%20such%20an%20accusation%20and%20present%20his%2Fher%20case%20in%20detail%2C%20without%20which%20the%20process%20of%20considering%20the%20veracity%20of%20that%20accusation%20may%20stand%20vitiated%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20If%20an%20accused%20person%20were%20to%20be%20penalised%2C%20the%20penalty%20needs%20to%20be%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20extent%20the%20accusation%20is%20established%20beyond%20all%20doubt%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20The%20expulsion%20of%20a%20member%20of%20any%20legislature%20is%20a%20serious%20matter%20which%20has%20wider%20implications%20for%20our%20democracy.%20It%20calls%20for%20a%20careful%20examination%20and%20circumspection%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20the%20other%20legislative%20bodies%20before%20such%20a%20far%20reaching%20decision%20is%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%