0Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20refuting%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20claim.%20The%20BRS%20has%20been%20specifically%20targeting%20Congress%20for%20its%20alleged%20inability%20to%20provide%2024-hour%20power%20supply%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20five%20guarantees%20promised%20by%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20reach%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20party%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20it%20was%20because%20of%20the%20obstacles%20set%20up%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20boosted%20the%20sagging%20morale%20of%20the%20Congress%20cadre%20and%20supporters%20in%20Telangana%20going%20by%20huge%20turnout%20at%20election%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K.%20Nageshwar%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%2C%20says%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20has%20helped%20the%20Congress%20to%20change%20the%20negative%20perception%20people%20had%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Telangana%20that%20days%20of%20the%20party%20were%20over%20in%20the%20state.%20Otherwise%2C%20consecutive%20defeats%20suffered%20by%20Congress%20in%20byelections%20to%20the%20Assembly%20created%20a%20perception%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20that%20the%20party%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20force.%20Worse%20still%2C%20it%20won%20only%20two%20out%20of%20150%20divisions%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20elections.%20But%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20feeling%20that%20Congress%20has%20revived%2C%20Nageshwar%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20professor%20and%20president%20of%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samiti%20M.%20Kodandaram%20echoes%20Nageshwar%E2%80%99s%20observation%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20had%20lost%20confidence%20in%20Congress%20prior%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20elections.%20Now%2C%20they%20see%20Congress%20as%20the%20only%20alternative%20to%20ruling%20BRS.%20They%20want%20an%20elected%20government%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Karnataka.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20dethroned%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20stands%20no%20chance%20in%20the%20present%20scenario%20in%20Telangana%2C%20says%20Kodandaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20been%20making%20a%20frontal%20attack%20against%20Congress%20primarily%20on%20two%20counts%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20five%20guarantees%20as%20well%20as%20the%20apparent%20power%20outages%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684916%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40DKShivakumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%E2%80%99%20friendly%20party%20in%20Karnataka%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20has%20joined%20the%20row%20to%20mount%20criticism%20against%20Congress.%20Its%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20H.%20D.%20Kumaraswamy%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20not%20to%20be%20carried%20away%20by%20Congress%20guarantees%20as%20they%20were%20an%20eyewash%20in%20his%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20ridiculed%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20for%20campaigning%20on%20behalf%20of%20Congress%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20surplus%E2%80%9D%20Telangana%20while%20the%20supply%20was%20a%20meagre%20two%20hours%20out%20of%20the%20promised%20five%20hours%20for%20agriculture%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Shivakumar%20urged%20people%20during%20their%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20to%20visit%20Karnataka%20to%20see%20for%20themselves%20the%20development%20model%20and%20five-hour%20power%20supply%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20new%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20offer%20to%20the%20next%20level%20was%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20who%20promised%20to%20facilitate%20the%20visit%20by%20arranging%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20come%20up%20with%20six%20guarantees%20in%20Telangana%20but%20they%20became%20a%20tool%20for%20BRS%20to%20launch%20the%20attack%20against%20the%20rival%20party.%20In%20tune%20with%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20observation%2C%20BRS%20working%20president%20K.%20T.%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20his%20Cabinet%20colleague%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20also%20said%20the%20guarantees%20were%20given%20a%20go-by%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20of%20Kumaraswamy%20invited%20criticism%20from%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20alleged%20the%20role%20of%20BRS%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20claimed%20that%20Harish%20Rao%20brought%20pressure%20on%20newspapers%20and%20news%20channels%20to%20play%20up%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20media%20conference%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reddy%2C%20it%20was%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Congress%20campaign%2C%20which%20has%20been%20highlighting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfailures%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BRS%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20the%20critical%20power%20situation%20since%20the%20Congress%20assumed%20power%20in%20Karnataka%20to%20show%20the%20party%20in%20a%20poor%20light%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20Chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20maintained%20that%20Congress%20could%20not%20win%20Telangana%20as%20conditions%20in%20the%20two%20states%20differed%20vastly.%20He%20pointed%20out%20the%20poor%20power%20position%20in%20Karnataka%20as%20against%2024-hour%20quality%20supply%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20farmers%20from%20Karnataka%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20expressing%20their%20ire%20against%20Congress%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20at%20Kodangal%20where%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20seeking%20election.%20Another%20bigger%20show%20by%20them%20is%20scheduled%20on%20November%2022%20at%20Hyderabad%20but%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20not%20yet%20given%20permission.%20The%20Congress%20claimed%20that%20the%20BRS%20was%20behind%20both%20the%20events%20though%20the%20permission%20on%20November%2022%20was%20sought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Karnataka%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20outcry%20against%20guarantees%20and%20power%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20were%20also%20behind%20the%20scene%20political%20developments%20in%20Congress%20which%20reinforced%20the%20position%20of%20party%20leadership%20from%20Karnataka%20as%20a%20strong%C2%A0%20player%20in%20the%20November%2030%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20the%20the%20party%20was%20sending%20crores%20of%20rupees%20from%20Karnataka%20to%20fund%20election%20in%20Telangana%20assumed%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20called%20on%20Shivakumar%20in%20Bengaluru%20twice%2C%20on%20one%20occasion%20reportedly%20to%20request%20him%20to%20camp%20in%20Telangana%20till%20the%20elections%20and%20another%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20BRS%20leader%20Tummala%20Nageswara%20Rao%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20and%20contest%20from%20Khammam.%20As%20a%20poll%20strategist%2C%20Shivakumar%20was%20tasked%20with%20dissidence%20management%20by%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20in%20the%20last%20Assembly%20elections%20of%20Telangana.%20He%20was%20among%2060-odd%20leaders%20from%20Karnataka%20who%20were%20roped%20in%20for%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSR%20Telangana%20president%20Sharmila%20Reddy%20also%20met%20him%20thrice%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%20to%20discuss%20her%20association%20with%20Congress.%20She%20may%20be%20offered%20membership%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Karnataka%20as%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20political%20grapevine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15165404%2FThe-Wire-81.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-the-performance-of-congress-govt-in-karnataka-has-emerged-as-a-key-talking-point%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20has%20boosted%20the%20morale%20of%20Congress%20cadres%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20alleged%20failures%20of%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20is%20being%20used%20by%20the%20ruling%20BRS%20to%20attack%20the%20rival%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-the-performance-of-congress-govt-in-karnataka-has-emerged-as-a-key-talking-point%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jennifer%20Aniston%20shares%20text%20from%20Matthew%20Perry%20as%20co-stars%20pay%20tribute%20to%20actor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-matthew-perry-jennifer-aniston_6342826.jpg%3F20231031130752%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffriends-stars-jennifer-aniston-and-david-schwimmer-pay-tribute-to-matthew-perry-13008769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Friends%20stars%20Jennifer%20Aniston%2C%20Lisa%20Kudrow%20and%20David%20Schwimmer%20have%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Matthew%20Perry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A685%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffriends-stars-jennifer-aniston-and-david-schwimmer-pay-tribute-to-matthew-perry-13008769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffriends-stars-jennifer-aniston-and-david-schwimmer-pay-tribute-to-matthew-perry-13008769%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffriends-stars-jennifer-aniston-and-david-schwimmer-pay-tribute-to-matthew-perry-13008769%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20Inventory%20Days%20for%20Consumer%20Goods%20as%20Low%20Demand%20Causes%20Supply%20Chain%20Congestion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15171005%2F1024px-Supermarket_full_of_goods.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Persistent%20low%20demand%20in%20the%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%20sector%20is%20causing%20supply%20chain%20congestion%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20stocks%20accumulating%20at%20distributors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fsupply-chain-clogs-up-for-consumer-items-as-festive-demand-muted-123111400958_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20distributors%20are%20extending%20credit%20terms%20up%20to%2045%20days%20to%20retailers%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20as%20there%E2%80%99s%20stress%20in%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20consumers%20are%20purchasing%20goods%2C%20distributors%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20major%20brands%20are%20experiencing%20a%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20some%20food%20sector%20companies%20seeing%20up%20to%2060%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFestival%20season%20demand%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20respite%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20summer%20wedding%20season%20remained%20weak%2C%20causing%20a%20build-up%20in%20inventory%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20One%20has%20to%20see%20how%20demand%20plays%20out%20after%20the%20rabi%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20distributor%20based%20in%20the%20east%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20distributor%20mentioned%20that%2C%20although%20he%20did%20not%20extend%20credit%20to%20retailers%2C%20he%20opted%20to%20sell%20lower%20stocks%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2020%25%20drop%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRetailers%20have%20been%20asking%20for%20higher%20credit%20days%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20sell%20lower%20stock%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20same%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20India%2C%20inventory%20days%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%20around%2040%20days%2C%20which%20is%20typically%2015%20days%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20distributor%20in%20North%20India%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20festival%20season%2C%20demand%20has%20been%20down%20by%2030-35%25%20compared%20to%20the%20average%20Diwali%20offtake%20that%20we%20witness.%20Gift%20packs%2C%20which%20see%20high%20demand%20during%20this%20time%2C%20have%20not%20sold%20well%2C%20nor%20have%20beverages%20or%20namkeens%20(salty%20snacks)%2C%20which%20typically%20witness%20a%20strong%20pick-up%20during%20this%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20to%20retailers%20for%20fast-moving%20stock-keeping%20units%20is%20at%2025%E2%80%9326%20days.%20This%20typically%20means%20retailers%20clear%20payments%20to%20distributors%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20days.%20For%20slow-moving%20items%2C%20credit%20days%20have%20increased%20to%2035-40%20days%20from%2015-20%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20inventory%20pile-up%20amid%20lack%20of%20demand%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20reports%20released%20by%20NIQ%20(formerly%20known%20as%20NielsenIQ)%20and%20Bizom%2C%20which%20reported%20a%20growth%20in%20the%20FMCG%20industry%2C%20in%20both%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20this%20observation%2C%20citing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Ffmcg-growth-up-in-sep-qtr-signs-of-rural-recovery-seen-11699379228097.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRural%2520markets%2520reported%2520a%25206.4%2Cperiod%252C%2520NIQ%2520said%2520on%2520Tuesday.%5C%22%3ENIQ%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20said%20that%20rural%20markets%20showed%20%E2%80%9Csigns%20of%20recovery%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20consumption%20picking%20up%20in%20the%20September%20quarter%20compared%20to%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20while%20urban%20markets%20maintained%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstable%20rate%20of%20consumption%20growth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20goods%20sales%20(without%20considering%20branded%20commodities)%20in%20urban%20areas%20grew%20by%201.6%25%2C%20while%20rural%20areas%20witnessed%20a%20substantial%20increase%20of%2010.2%25%2C%20Bizom%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20slowdown%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20the%20big%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CObviously%20there%20is%20a%20slowdown%20as%20far%20as%20FMCG%20is%20concerned.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20clear%20slowdown%20in%20rural.%20Despite%20us%20continuing%20to%20get%20deeper%20into%20rural%20areas%2C%20getting%20into%20more%20villages%2C%20etc.%2C%20we%20have%20started%20to%20see%20the%20rural%20economy%20to%20splutter%20a%20bit.%20However%2C%20these%20are%20macro%20issues%20which%20companies%20like%20us%20cannot%20sort%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20Berry%2C%20executive%20vice-chairman%20and%20managing%20director%2C%20Britannia%20Industries%20Ltd%2C%20said%20during%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20post%20earnings%20call%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Frural-demand-slows-down-for-fmcg-11699029760068.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarico%20said%20that%20while%20urban%20sentiment%20improved%20sequentially%2C%20instances%20of%20higher%20food%20inflation%20and%20uneven%20rainfall%20distribution%20led%20to%20a%20slower-than-expected%20pace%20of%20recovery%20in%20rural%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaugata%20Gupta%2C%20Marico%20MD%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20rural%20demand%20continues%20to%20lag%20urban.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20said%20that%2C%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20volume%20growth%2C%20demand%20is%20not%20the%20only%20factor.%20There%20are%20other%20things%20that%20have%20happened.%20There%20has%20been%20some%20inflation%20and%20some%20down%20trading%20and%20in%20some%20of%20our%20categories%2C%20that%20down%20trading%20can%20be%20to%20smaller%20brands%2C%20or%20to%20unbranded%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Dabur%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rural%20markets%20are%20lagging%20urban%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20PTI%20reported%20a%20decline%20in%20rural%20consumption%20due%20to%20persistent%20food%20inflation%20and%20uneven%20rains%20in%20some%20regions.%20It%20reported%20that%20the%20FMCG%20industry%20has%20witnessed%20a%20challenging%20September%20quarter%20amid%20subdued%20consumer%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Frural-demand-revival-what-new-data-tells-us-11698085155203.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20FY24%2C%20some%20of%20these%20companies%20have%20done%20well%2C%20while%20others%20have%20not.%20This%20has%20raised%20doubts%20about%20revival%20in%20rural%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20a%20third%20of%20consumer%20goods%20companies%E2%80%99%20revenues%20are%20attributed%20to%20rural%20demand%2C%20reflecting%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20rural%20economy.%20And%20a%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20lives%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20rural%20economy%E2%80%99s%20growth%20and%20development%20are%20crucial%20to%20the%20overall%20growth%20and%20inclusive%20development%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15171005%2F1024px-Supermarket_full_of_goods.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20distributors%20are%20extending%20credit%20terms%20up%20to%2045%20days%20to%20retailers%2C%20'Business%20Standard'%20reported.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20as%20there's%20stress%20in%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20consumers%20are%20purchasing%20goods%2C%20distributors%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Army%20claims%20foothold%20on%20bank%20of%20Dnipro%20river%20in%20south%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700047952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1423C%2Fproduction%2F_131729428_gettyimages-1773655376.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67424672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20admits%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20groups%E2%80%9D%20of%20Uk