ill%20continue%20until%20Hamas%20is%20eradicated.%20But%20his%20battle%20plan%20for%20achieving%20that%20objective%20is%20far%20from%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20calls%20grow%20louder%20around%20the%20world%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20Israel%20is%20finding%20itself%20under%20increasing%20pressure%20to%20respond.%20This%20is%20placing%20more%20scrutiny%20on%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20overall%20strategy%20for%20prosecuting%20the%20war%20%E2%80%93%20and%20what%20could%20happen%20after%20it%E2%80%99s%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstantly%20in%20the%20background%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20campaign%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20%E2%80%93%20Israelis%20and%20other%20nationals%20%E2%80%93%20held%20by%20Hamas.%20Netanyahu%20has%20said%20there%20will%20be%20no%20ceasefire%20until%20all%20the%20hostages%20are%20released.%20Hamas%20has%20responded%20that%20no%20hostages%20will%20be%20released%20in%20advance%20of%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20side%20shows%20signs%20of%20budging%20and%20Hamas%20has%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-11-13%2Fisrael-gaza-war-latest-updates-rafah-open-hamas-hostage-talks%2F103096500%5C%22%3Esuspended%20negotiations%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20hostage%20releases%20because%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20siege%20of%20Al%20Shifa%20hospital%2C%20Gaza%20City%E2%80%99s%20main%20medical%20centre.%20Israel%20says%20a%20Hamas%20complex%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F12%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fgaza-hospitals-shifa.html%5C%22%3Ehidden%20in%20tunnels%3C%2Fa%3E%20underneath%20the%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20Hamas%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20now%20crowded%20into%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20strip.%20Some%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20key%20leaders%20are%20likely%20hiding%20there%2C%20raising%20another%20pertinent%20question%20as%20the%20war%20drags%20on.%20How%20will%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20succeed%20in%20their%20mission%20of%20eradicating%20Hamas%20if%20its%20operatives%20are%20hiding%20among%20civilians%20in%20such%20a%20crowded%20area%3F%20Netanyahu%20has%20given%20no%20public%20indication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20US-Israeli%20frictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20key%20questions%20left%20unanswered%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20disconnect%20between%20Netanyahu%20and%20the%20Biden%20administration%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20have%20both%20said%20Israel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-opposes-israeli-occupation-post-conflict-gaza-white-house-2023-11-07%2F%5C%22%3Eshould%20not%20reoccupy%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war.%20They%20have%20also%20indicated%20a%20preference%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20led%20by%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fnation-world%2Fblinken-lays-out-possible-endgame-in-gaza-under-palestinian-authority%2F%5C%22%3Eextend%20its%20authority%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Gaza%20after%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20said%20Israel%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Flive-blog%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-hospitals-al-shifa-palestinians-rcna124737%5C%22%3Eneed%20to%20retain%3C%2Fa%3E%20control%20over%20security%20in%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.aawsat.com%2Farab-world%2F4663726-israel-says-palestinian-authority-current-form-should-not-run-gaza%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20as%20a%20successor%20administration%20to%20Hamas%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20it%20has%20not%20issued%20an%20unequivocal%20condemnation%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetanyahu%E2%80%99s%20balancing%20act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%E2%80%99s%20planning%20seems%20to%20be%20edging%20towards%20a%20demilitarised%20Gaza%20with%20IDF%20forces%20based%20outside%20the%20strip%2C%20ready%20to%20re-enter%20the%20enclave%20when%20any%20security%20threat%20to%20Israel%20is%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20addressing%20the%20risk%20that%20a%20power%20vacuum%20following%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20removal%20might%20be%20filled%20by%20another%20militant%20group%2C%20such%20as%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20which%20would%20certainly%20not%20be%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20has%20he%20addressed%20the%20probability%20that%20disarming%20those%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20already%20radicalised%20will%20only%20be%20a%20partially%20effective%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20understanding%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20thought%20process%20is%20that%20he%20is%20dealing%20with%20several%20imperatives%20simultaneously%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Appeasing%20hard-line%20members%20of%20his%20government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coalition%20government%20he%20leads%20is%20the%20most%20right-wing%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20history.%20Though%20the%20influence%20of%20extremists%20has%20been%20diluted%20by%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20centrist%20Benny%20Gantz%20to%20the%20war%20cabinet%2C%20Heritage%20Minister%20Amihai%20Eliyahu%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fisrael-minister-amichai-eliyahu-suspend-benjamin-netanyahu-nuclear-bomb-gaza-hamas-war%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DIsrael%2527s%2520Heritage%2520Minister%2520Amichai%2520Eliyahu%2Cthe%2520government%2520announced%2520on%2520Sunday.%5C%22%3Esuggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20Israel%20might%20use%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%20against%20Gaza.%20He%20was%20repudiated%20by%20Netanyahu%2C%20but%20the%20comment%20was%20indicative%20of%20hardline%20sentiment%20that%20remains%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20war%2C%20Netanyahu%20doubtless%20hopes%20to%20resume%20governing%20with%20this%20coalition%2C%20so%20he%20must%20take%20their%20interests%20into%20account%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20formulating%20a%20post-war%20plan%20for%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Assuaging%20the%20anger%20of%20hostages%E2%80%99%20families%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20are%20demanding%20Netanyahu%20prioritise%20negotiations%20to%20free%20their%20loved%20ones%20over%20the%20military%20campaign.%20Netanyahu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fmiddle-east-and-africa%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Fnetanyahus-handling-of-the-hostage-crisis-enrages-israelis%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20is%20prioritising%20both.%20But%20that%20claim%20has%20lost%20some%20cogency%20since%20reports%20emerged%20that%20Netanyahu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fnov%2F09%2Fnetanyahu-rejected-ceasefire-for-hostages-deal-in-gaza-sources-say%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20deal%20for%20a%20five-day%20ceasefire%20early%20in%20the%20war%20in%20return%20for%20release%20of%20some%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Securing%20his%20own%20political%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20will%20be%20acutely%20aware%20that%20the%20only%20other%20Israeli%20political%20leader%20to%20have%20presided%20over%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Freadingroom%2Fdocs%2F2012-12-10E.pdf%5C%22%3Esecurity%20and%20intelligence%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20magnitude%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20October%207%20attack%20was%20Golda%20Meir%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%20in%201973.%20And%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fisraeled.org%2Fgolda-meir-resigns-prime-minister%2F%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20the%20Egyptian%20and%20Syrian%20forces%20were%20defeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20the%20current%20war%20continues%2C%20the%20greater%20the%20chance%20Netanyahu%20can%20severely%20diminish%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20leadership%20structure.%20And%20this%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20burnish%20his%20tarnished%20credentials%20as%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20security%20guarantor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20also%20have%20noted%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Ehud%20Barak%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fehud-barak-israel-palestine-war-hamas-global-opinion-sours%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DTEL%2520AVIV%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520Israeli%2520Prime%2520Minister%2Cagainst%2520its%2520attacks%2520on%2520Gaza.%5C%22%3Ecomment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Israel%20probably%20has%20only%20weeks%20left%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%20before%20international%20public%20opinion%20completely%20turns%20against%20Israel.%20This%20adds%20urgency%20to%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20need%20for%20an%20outcome%20he%20can%20describe%20as%20a%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Dealing%20with%20pressures%20from%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20also%20letting%20it%20be%20known%20through%20media%20leaks%20that%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-11-06%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fgrowing-concern-in-wh-israel-has-no-exit-strategy-pa-in-no-rush-to-take-over-gaza%2F0000018b-a0d4-dc0b-a1cb-e5d6fc0e0000%5C%22%3Econcerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20of%20the%20war%2C%20particularly%20the%20high%20number%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20apparent%20lack%20of%20an%20exit%20strategy.%20The%20US%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-administration-warning-israel-gaza-civilians%2Findex.html%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3D2024%2520Election-%2CUS%2520warns%2520Israel%2520amid%2520Gaza%2520carnage%2520it%2520doesn%2Chave%2520long%2520before%2520support%2520erodes%26amp%3Btext%3DPresident%2520Joe%2520Biden%2520and%2520his%2Cscale%2520of%2520humanitarian%2520suffering%2520there%5C%22%3Ewarning%3C%2Fa%3E%20Israel%20more%20explicitly%20that%20international%20support%20for%20its%20military%20operation%20is%20waning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20of%20growing%20concern%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration%20because%20its%20strong%20support%20for%20Israel%20comes%20with%20increasing%20risks.%20First%2C%20American%20diplomats%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-diplomats-warn-middle-east-fury%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20anger%20in%20the%20Arab%20world%20is%20so%20intense%20over%20continued%20US%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Closing%20us%20Arab%20publics%20for%20a%20generation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20also%20the%20risk%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20Israel%20could%20hurt%20him%20during%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election.%20Many%20of%20the%20anti-war%20demonstrators%20in%20the%20US%20are%20young%2C%20college-educated%20progressives%20who%20helped%20elect%20Biden%20in%202020.%20If%20these%20voters%20fail%20to%20turn%20out%20for%20him%20next%20year%2C%20the%20likely%20Republican%20candidate%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20could%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaching%20an%20acceptable%20%E2%80%93%20and%20achievable%20%E2%80%93%20endgame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20and%20Netanyahu%20are%20thus%20on%20a%20collision%20course.%20Netanyahu%20wants%20a%20long%20war%20in%20order%20to%20maximise%20his%20chances%20of%20eliminating%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20delay%20the%20inevitable%20post-war%20reckoning%20over%20the%20Israeli%20security%20failure%20that%20led%20to%20so%20much%20carnage%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20agrees%20Hamas%20has%20to%20be%20destroyed%2C%20but%20he%20needs%20the%20war%20to%20be%20as%20short%20as%20possible%20in%20order%20to%20limit%20the%20blow-back%20against%20US%20int