nod%20Adani%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVinod%20Adani%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98promoter%20group%E2%80%99%20of%20various%20listed%20entities%20within%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20Indians%20who%20obtained%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20are%20industrialist%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20and%20his%20wife%20Radhika%20Oswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Oswal%2C%20is%20founder%20of%20Burrup%20Holdings%20Limited%2C%20a%20liquid%20ammonium%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20in%20the%20news%20recently%20for%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-tycoon-pankaj-oswal-buys-one-of-the-worlds-most-expensive-houses-for-rs-1-649-crore-in-switzerland-11687886475271.html%5C%22%3E%20purchasing%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20houses%20in%20Switzerland%20for%20%24200%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOtis%20data%20contains%20numerous%20documents%20related%20to%20Cyprol%20Limited%2C%20the%20company%20established%20by%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20as%20well%20as%20details%20of%20his%20citizenship%20application%20and%20final%20approval.%20The%20Oswals%20applied%20for%20citizenship%20on%20April%2028%2C%202017%2C%20and%20it%20was%20granted%20almost%20a%20year%20later%20on%20April%204%2C%202018%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20once%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20obtained%20his%20Cypriot%20citizenship%2C%20he%20shut%20down%20Cyprol%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20proof%20of%20this%20is%20the%20authorisation%20he%20signed%20as%20the%20Ultimate%20Beneficial%20Owner%20(UBO)%20of%20the%20company%20for%20ConnectedSky%2C%20on%20March%2022%2C%202019%20to%20strike%20off%20the%20company%20from%20the%20Cyprus%20registry%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConnectedSky%20is%20one%20of%20the%20six%20financial%20service%20providers%20which%20over%20270%20investigative%20reporters%2